orders to use the cannons...

107
00:12:09,410 --> 00:12:12,680
Finishing the enthronement without
a problem is most important,

108
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,979
so hold off on using the cannons.

109
00:12:14,589 --> 00:12:17,420
