00:54:33,049 --> 00:54:35,879
So? What is next?

539
00:54:36,220 --> 00:54:37,290
I wish...

540
00:54:38,350 --> 00:54:41,060
to share my power with every
single one of the people...

541
00:54:41,720 --> 00:54:44,029
so they can be stronger than
me when they come together.

542
00:54:44,759 --> 00:54:48,600
That way, the corrupt shall never
be able to exploit them again.

543
00:54:49,299 --> 00:54:51,799
I believe that is how
this difficult battle...

544
00:54:53,700 --> 00:54:55,399
and this wonder-filled journey...

545
00:54:56,540 --> 00:54:57,970
should end.

546
00:54:58,640 --> 00:55:00,779
So you are saying I'll be even busier now.

547
00:55:00,779 --> 00:55:02,640
Let us call it a day.

548
00:55:02,640 --> 00:55:04,209
My goodness.

549
00:55:06,980 --> 00:55:08,919
Let us just go home.

550
00:55:08,919 --> 00:55:10,649
You can go through that tomorrow morning.

551
00:55:11,350 --> 00:55:12,890
We just don't click.

552
00:55:15,060 --> 00:55:16,459
But you should tidy up before...

553
00:55:16,629 --> 00:55:18,129
- Have a restful night.
- Will do.

554
00:55:19,290 --> 00:55:22,000
Du Il, you need to organize...

555
00:55:22,259 --> 00:55:23,299
Du Il!

556
00:55:23,629 --> 00:55:25,569
Gosh, that punk.

557
00:55:49,419 --> 00:55:52,160
THE QUEEN'S DICTIONARY

558
00:56:01,239 --> 00:56:03,439
Did I lose something?

559
00:56:06,879 --> 00:56:08,810
From time to time, I feel...

560
00:56:12,279 --> 00:56:13,419
He did it.

561
00:56:14,120 --> 00:56:15,319
He managed to pull it off.

562
00:56:15,319 --> 00:56:16,350
THE ERA OF KING CHEOLJO'S DIRECT RULE

563
00:56:29,160 --> 00:56:32,899
THE ANNALS OF KING CHEOLJO

564
00:56:37,109 --> 00:56:38,109
My Queen.

565
00:56:43,040 --> 00:56:44,350
Is this not funny?

566
00:57:06,029 --> 00:57:07,100
Jang Bong Hwan!

567
00:57:11,540 --> 00:57:12,609
Don't come closer.

568
00:57:14,839 --> 00:57:16,580
I must find Secretary Han first.

569
00:57:16,980 --> 00:57:19,649
No, would it be the fastest to
just go directly to the media?

570
00:57:20,549 --> 00:57:23,549
Why are you running away?
You did a good deed!

571
00:57:24,790 --> 00:57:25,850
"Good deed"?

572
00:57:27,319 --> 00:57:29,359
Then why are you keeping tabs on me?

573
00:57:29,989 --> 00:57:31,359
No, we're trying to protect you because...

574
00:57:31,359 --> 00:57:33,129
you sent us a tip for the
sake of public interest.

575
00:57:33,459 --> 00:57:34,459
"Public interest"?

576
00:57:34,459 --> 00:57:37,770
Well, remember the CCTV
camera in the food storage?

577
00:57:37,770 --> 00:57:39,529
You fixed it in secret.

578
00:57:40,000 --> 00:57:41,069
I did?

579
00:57:47,839 --> 00:57:48,839
Hold on.

580
00:57:57,089 --> 00:57:58,890
Do you manage the CCTV camera?

581
00:57:59,819 --> 00:58:01,859
It's odd that it keeps breaking.

582
00:58:02,259 --> 00:58:03,459
I must catch this thief.

583
00:58:05,089 --> 00:58:07,060
Why did you do something so useless?

584
00:58:07,359 --> 00:58:08,759
This is very unlike you.

585
00:58:08,759 --> 00:58:11,569
There you are. Why didn't you
come sooner to tell me this?

586
00:58:12,169 --> 00:58:13,700
I already got myself in trouble.

587
00:58:14,470 --> 00:58:16,040
- What?
- I sent the CCTV footage...

588
00:58:16,040 --> 00:58:19,140
to the media for free,
which is very unlike me.

589
00:58:21,339 --> 00:58:23,379
He's lying.

590
00:58:23,750 --> 00:58:24,850
Yes, I'm sure.

591
00:58:25,350 --> 00:58:28,680
The Jang Bong Hwan I know
doesn't care about justice.

592
00:58:28,680 --> 00:58:30,520
He'd come to me and try...

593
00:58:30,520 --> 00:58:33,959
to strike a deal before going
to the media. Am I wrong?

594
00:58:36,120 --> 00:58:37,129
You're right.

595
00:58:38,089 --> 00:58:39,330
That's the kind of jerk that I am.

596
00:58:40,100 --> 00:58:41,129
But you know what?

597
00:58:42,399 --> 00:58:44,230
- I've changed.
- Really?

598
00:58:45,069 --> 00:58:46,529
- Why?
- No idea.

599
00:58:47,239 --> 00:58:48,470
I just wanted to do it.

600
00:58:52,770 --> 00:58:53,980
You scumbag!

601
00:59:00,350 --> 00:59:01,379
Chef Bu!

602
00:59:03,020 --> 00:59:04,089
Chef Bu!

603
00:59:06,220 --> 00:59:08,589
- Darn it.
- You jerk!

604
00:59:19,169 --> 00:59:21,870
Cheoljong managed to change his fate,

605
00:59:22,169 --> 00:59:23,370
and I've changed too.

606
00:59:25,209 --> 00:59:27,009
Then how come Secretary
Han is still the same?

607
00:59:31,250 --> 00:59:32,680
BOOK BROWSER

608
00:59:34,819 --> 00:59:36,720
CHEOLJO

609
00:59:37,819 --> 00:59:40,759
Don't tell me the world didn't change at all.

610
00:59:41,390 --> 00:59:43,560
Are Cheoljong and I the
only ones that changed?

611
00:59:43,560 --> 00:59:44,660
"THE VERITABLE RECORDS
OF THE JOSEON DYNASTY"

612
00:59:44,660 --> 00:59:46,629
CHEOLJO'S ACHIEVEMENTS

613
00:59:46,629 --> 00:59:48,600
"CHEOLJO'S GENTLE CHARISMA
SHOOK JOSEON TO ITS VERY CORE"

614
00:59:48,600 --> 00:59:50,629
"CHEOLJO LED THE REFORM WITH THE PEOPLE"

615
00:59:50,629 --> 00:59:53,000
"KING CHEOLJO AND QUEEN
CHEORIN'S ACHIEVEMENTS"

616
00:59:53,000 --> 00:59:54,569
"SERVED AS MODEL FOR PRO-REFORM KINGS"

617
00:59:54,569 --> 00:59:56,939
"CHEOLJO LAID THE FOUNDATION FOR DEMOCRACY"

618
00:59:59,169 --> 01:00:01,209
- A comment, please.
- Say a few words!

619
01:00:01,209 --> 01:00:03,379
- Say a few words!
- Do you admit all the charges?

620
01:00:03,379 --> 01:00:05,350
- Over here!
- Just a comment, please!

621
01:00:05,350 --> 01:00:07,779
- Is it all true?
- Do you admit all the charges?

622
01:00:07,779 --> 01:00:10,020
- Are the allegations true?
- Is it all true?

623
01:00:10,020 --> 01:00:16,060
SECRETARY HAN PYO JIN COMMITTED
EMBEZZLEMENT FOR YEARS

624
01:00:19,959 --> 01:00:21,430
History goes on, and things change.

625
01:00:21,430 --> 01:00:25,100
But those conniving rats who engage
in corruption always survive.

626
01:00:27,169 --> 01:00:29,770
Maybe a good world isn't
completely devoid of rotten parts,

627
01:00:29,770 --> 01:00:32,509
but it allows us to cut out
such corrupt, rotten segments.

628
01:00:34,009 --> 01:00:36,540
If you keep trying to change
your life for the better,

629
01:00:36,540 --> 01:00:38,410
you'll bring about positive
change to the world,

630
01:00:39,450 --> 01:00:41,580
just like Cheoljong and I did.

631
01:01:00,899 --> 01:01:02,939
- Your Majesty.
- Yes.

632
01:01:02,939 --> 01:01:04,239
It's upside down.

633
01:01:05,009 --> 01:01:06,040
Oh, right.

634
01:01:11,109 --> 01:01:14,120
Your Majesty, are you
having trouble focusing?

635
01:01:14,649 --> 01:01:16,750
I wish to see my Queen so much...

636
01:01:17,390 --> 01:01:18,919
that I cannot focus.

637
01:01:22,419 --> 01:01:23,560
This is not good.

638
01:01:24,230 --> 01:01:26,589
I should go see my Queen first,
then focus on this later.

639
01:01:28,299 --> 01:01:29,299
Next.

640
01:01:30,230 --> 01:01:32,600
All women in the Internal Court
who are over the age of 18...

641
01:01:33,640 --> 01:01:35,169
are permitted to wed.

642
01:01:41,209 --> 01:01:42,209
Yes, Your Highness.

643
01:01:42,209 --> 01:01:45,180
Also, no one under the age of 10...

644
01:01:45,180 --> 01:01:47,379
should be accepted into the
Internal Court as a court maid.

645
01:01:49,779 --> 01:01:50,890
And...

646
01:01:54,790 --> 01:01:57,160
What is next, Your Highness?

647
01:02:01,259 --> 01:02:02,299
Your Highness?

648
01:02:05,169 --> 01:02:06,430
I'm sorry, Court Lady Choi.

649
01:02:06,430 --> 01:02:09,270
I see that you are having trouble focusing.

650
01:02:09,569 --> 01:02:11,939
It has only been a little while
since you last saw His Majesty.

651
01:02:12,540 --> 01:02:14,439
It is not me. My baby misses him.

652
01:02:15,140 --> 01:02:16,480
For the baby's wellbeing,

653
01:02:16,779 --> 01:02:20,109
