His Majesty for a moment?

654
01:02:20,450 --> 01:02:21,580
I wholeheartedly agree.

655
01:02:26,450 --> 01:02:27,520
- Your Majesty.
- Yes.

656
01:02:27,520 --> 01:02:30,830
Her Highness is headed to
the Seonjeongjeon Hall.

657
01:02:31,759 --> 01:02:34,259
Oh, no. We just missed each other.

658
01:02:37,200 --> 01:02:38,830
His Majesty is at the Daejojeon Hall?

659
01:02:39,129 --> 01:02:40,169
Yes, Your Highness.

660
01:02:47,779 --> 01:02:49,779
Wait for us, Your Highness!

661
01:02:50,509 --> 01:02:52,750
Look how excited she is. My gosh.

662
01:03:00,589 --> 01:03:03,220
Oh, no. Did we miss each other again?

663
01:03:04,290 --> 01:03:07,359
My goodness, are we playing
hide-and-seek or what?

664
01:03:15,399 --> 01:03:16,500
This is not working.

665
01:03:17,540 --> 01:03:18,640
In that case...

666
01:03:32,290 --> 01:03:33,790
Finally, we meet.

667
01:03:34,319 --> 01:03:35,359
After...

668
01:03:37,330 --> 01:03:39,290
missing each other so many times.

669
01:03:39,790 --> 01:03:44,299
Those fleeting moments felt like an eternity.

670
01:04:16,259 --> 01:04:20,299
By the way, why do you keep talking
to me so formally these days?

671
01:04:20,939 --> 01:04:23,100
Are you plotting something
to surprise me again?

672
